      <title>布林肯在新的中东之行中将重点关注加沙的下一步发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/what-s-next-for-gaza-is-blinken-s-focus-on-new-mideast-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国高级官员表示，国务卿安东尼·布林肯将利用自以色列与哈马斯冲突爆发以来的第四次中东之行，重点关注加沙地带的未来治理，同时也寻求遏制以色列与哈马斯冲突的威胁。更广泛的地区战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/what-s-next-for-gaza-is-blinken-s-focus-on-new-mideast-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 20:03:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将特朗普对民主的威胁视为 2024 年的核心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-casts-trump-threat-to-democracy-as-central-to-2024-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统将 2024 年大选视为事关美国民主的一场选举，他利用今年的第一次竞选活动警告选民不要让前任唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-casts-trump-threat-to-democracy-as-central-to-2024-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全国步枪协会主席拉皮埃尔在民事审判前夕宣布辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/nra-chief-lapierre-announces-resignation-on-eve-of-civil-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韦恩·拉皮埃尔 (Wayne LaPierre) 辞去美国全国步枪协会首席执行官一职，此前该协会的财务状况一直存在争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/nra-chief-lapierre-announces-resignation-on-eve-of-civil-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:39:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国前能源部长斯基德莫尔因苏纳克受挫而辞去议员职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/ex-minister-skidmore-resigns-tory-whip-in-setback-for-uk-s-sunak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国前能源部长从执政的议会保守党辞职，以抗议里希·苏纳克允许进一步石油和天然气钻探的计划，这对正在准备今年晚些时候大选的首相来说是一个新的挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/ex-minister-skidmore-resigns-tory-whip-in-setback-for-uk-s-sunak</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 18:37:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>州政府辩称，特朗普因欺诈欠纽约人 3.7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州告诉一名法官，最终将对民事欺诈案做出判决，唐纳德·特朗普及其公司应被责令支付 3.7 亿美元，高于 2.5 亿美元，因为十多年来在财务记录中夸大了他的资产价值审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普聘请德克萨斯州堕胎法背后的律师进行最高法院选票斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-ballot-fight-at-supreme-court-led-by-texan-behind-abortion-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州律师设计了该州为期六周的堕胎法，允许普通公民向违法者寻求 10,000 美元的赏金，该律师已被唐纳德·特朗普聘请，帮助他在美国最高法院争取留在总统选票上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-ballot-fight-at-supreme-court-led-by-texan-behind-abortion-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚议员表示对丹格特的袭击将损害经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/nigerian-lawmaker-says-raid-on-tycoon-dangote-will-hurt-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚议会一个有影响力的小组主席表示，尼日利亚反腐败官员对亿万富翁阿里科·丹格特控制的丹格特工业有限公司的办公室进行突击搜查，将损害经济并吓退投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/nigerian-lawmaker-says-raid-on-tycoon-dangote-will-hurt-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:26:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油资源丰富的索马里地区在紧张局势中选举领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/oil-rich-puntland-region-of-somalia-elects-leader-amid-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[邦特兰是索马里东部石油资源丰富的半自治领土，将于 1 月 8 日在议会投票中选出新总统，此时摩加迪沙正忙着试图控制索马里兰的分裂地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/oil-rich-puntland-region-of-somalia-elects-leader-amid-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 14:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于法院阻碍反对党领袖的出价，塞内加尔债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/senegal-bonds-fall-as-court-stymies-opposition-leader-s-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔的欧洲债券下跌，此前最高法院维持了该国主要反对派领导人的诽谤罪定罪，从技术上讲，这将取消奥斯曼·桑科在下个月选举中竞选总统的资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/senegal-bonds-fall-as-court-stymies-opposition-leader-s-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 12:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非运动员奥斯卡·皮斯托利斯假释出狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-05/south-african-athlete-oscar-pistorius-to-be-released-on-parole-after-nearly-9-years-in-prison</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非比勒陀利亚（美联社）——奥运会短跑运动员奥斯卡·皮斯托利斯 (Oscar Pistorius) 是一位双截肢者，他在骑着碳纤维刀片跑步时成为了这项运动最高水平的全球明星。他因杀害女友模特瑞娃·斯汀坎普 (Reeva Steenkamp) 服刑近九年，于周五出狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-05/south-african-athlete-oscar-pistorius-to-be-released-on-parole-after-nearly-9-years-in-prison</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 05:59:04 GMT</pubDate>
